I. Overall technical point to keep in mind

The invention should not be presented only as “generating a personalized shadow.” I think the stronger technical explanation is:

The invention provides a virtual-rendering pipeline where user/media inputs and virtual-environment inputs are converted into contextual vectors/contextual image, and that contextual image is transformed using the avatar’s base-shadow attributes such as orientation and dimension to generate a personalized/transfigured shadow rendered with the avatar.
